body:

!!! info
    **Want to test Zenodo?** Use our sandbox environment on [https://sandbox.zenodo.org](https://sandbox.zenodo.org) to play.

The following section explains how you submit a **published record** to a community for inclusion.

##### Only published records

You can only submit published records for inclusion in a community (see [submit for review](../submit-for-review/) for submitting an unpublished record to a community).

##### Both uploader and curators can edit

Both you as the uploader and the curators of the community can edit the metadata when you submit it to a community.

Learn below how to:
